ييًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (K.) ―         -b5-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "kalimapN tamolaA^u Alfama", "text_ar": "كَلِمَةٌ تَمْلَاُ الفَمَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A word,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "saying, that fills the mouth;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] i. e.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "gross, and abominable; not allowable to be spoken; that fills the mouth so that it cannot articulate."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA, from a trad.) ―         -b6-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_imolaw^uwA A^afowaA'akumo mina AlquroA=ni", "text_ar": "اـِمْلَوُوا اَفْوَاءَكُمْ مِنَ القُرْا=نِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Fill your mouths with the Kur-án"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (TA.) ―         -b7-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "muliy^a ruEobFA", "text_ar": "مُلِيَ رُعْبًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maluw^a rEbA", "text_ar": "مَلُوَ رعبا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He was filled with fright."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A.) ―         -b8-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "malaA^a viyaAbiY", "text_ar": "مَلَاَ ثِيَابِى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He sprinkled my clothes with mud, &c."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A.)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "malaA^a raAkibahu", "text_ar": "مَلَاَ رَاكِبَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a camel)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "bespattered his rider"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "with his ejected cud]. (S, K, art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zrd", "text_ar": "زرد"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".) ―         -b9-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "malaA^a", "text_ar": "مَلَاَ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EinaAnahu", "text_ar": "عِنَانَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He made,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "urged, his beast to run vehemently."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "En", "text_ar": "عن"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".) ―         -b10-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "muliy^a", "text_ar": "مُلِيَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", like"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EuniYa", "text_ar": "عُنِىَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", [i. e., pass. in form, but neut. in signification,] and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maluw^a", "text_ar": "مَلُوَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He had the disease called"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mulaA='ap", "text_ar": "مُلَا=ءَة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (A, K.) ―         -b11-  See 3."}], "source_refs": ["S", "K"]}, {"entry_id": "n38833", "headword_ar": "مَلَاٌ", "root": "mlA^a", "body": [{"kind": "italic_en", "text": "An assembly,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(IAar, S, K,) absolutely, (TA,) [whether of nobles or others]: pl."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^amolaA='N", "text_ar": "اَمْلَا=ءٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (IAar.) ―         -b2-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Nobles; chiefs; princes;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "syn."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^a$oraAfN", "text_ar": "اَشْرَافٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EiloyapN", "text_ar": "عِلْيَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (K;)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "principal persons; persons whose opinion is respected."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) ("}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlmalaA^u AlA^aEloYa", "text_ar": "المَلَاُ الاَعلْىَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The most exalted princes;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e.]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the angels that are admitted near"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to the presence of God"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the archangels."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "TA.) See"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "samEahu", "text_ar": "سَمعَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", for other explanations. ―         -b3-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A people of comely appearance, figure, attire,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "adornment, united for some purpose"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "design;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "expl. by"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qawomN *w Al$~aArapi wAlt~ajam~uEi liloA_iraAdapi", "text_ar": "قَوْمٌ ذو الشَّارَةِ والتَّجَمُّعِ لِلْاـِرَادَةِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (Abu-l-Hasan, K:) [but this is wrong, see Beyd,"}, {"kind": "page_break", "n": 2730}, {"kind": "text", "text": "ii. 247.] Thus it is of a different class from"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "rahaTN", "text_ar": "رَهَطٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", though, like this word, a quasi-pl. n. It is an epithet in which the quality of a substantive predominates. (Abu-l-Hasan.) ―         -b4-  (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Consultation."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K.) [You say,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maA kaAna h`*aA AlA^amoru Eano malaA_K min~aA", "text_ar": "مَا كَانَ هٰذَا الاَمْرُ عَنْ مَلَاـٍ مِنَّا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "This thing was not the result of a consultation and consent on our part:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[and]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^akaAna h`*aA Eano", "text_ar": "اَكَانَ هٰذَا عَنْ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "malaA_K minokumo", "text_ar": "مَلَاـٍ مِنْكُمْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Was this the result of a consultation of your nobles, and of your assembly?"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "said by 'Omar when he was stabbed: asserted to be tropical in this sense by Z and others. (TA.)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taHad~avuwA malaA^F", "text_ar": "تَحَدَّثُوا مَلَاً"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "They conversed, consulting together."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S.) ―         -b5-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Opinion."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K.) [See a supposed example below.] ―         -b6-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Disposition; nature; manners;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K;)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a nature rich in needful qualities:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(T:) pl."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^amolaA='N", "text_ar": "اَمْلَا=ءٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (S.) [You say,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maA A^aHosana malaA^a baniY fulaAnK", "text_ar": "مَا اَحْسَنَ مَلَاَ بَنِى فُلَانٍ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "How good are the dispositions,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "manners, and conversation, of the sons of such a one!"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S.) ElJuhanee says,"}, {"kind": "quote", "text": "tanaAdawoA yaAla buhovapa A_i*o raA^awonaA\n                     \n                     \n                        faqulonaA A^aHosiniY malaA^F juhayonaA"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S) ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "They called out, one to another, O Buhtheh! come to our aid! when they saw us: and we said,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Be of good disposition,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "manners, O Juheyneh!"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or, accord. to some,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Be of good opinion, O Juheyneh!"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(see above:) or, as some say,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Aid well, O Juheyneh!"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "taking"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mlA^", "text_ar": "ملا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "in the sense of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mumaAlaA^apF", "text_ar": 